frames.caption: In a serene, moonlit setting, two anthropomorphic white cats stand outside a traditional wooden house. One cat, wearing a pink dress, gently cradles a black kitten, while the other, dressed in casual attire with a bag, stands attentively. A warm light from a hanging lantern casts a soft glow over the scene, highlighting the tranquility of their interaction.
